          <li>Boilover cleanup priced like igniter replacement</li>
          <li>Gas safety check as separate add-on</li>
          <li>You don&rsquo;t know what the part costs</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="tr-card us">
        <h3>Our approach &mdash; labor + parts separate</h3>
        <ul class="tr-list">
          <li>Diagnose first, then quote</li>
          <li>Drying job vs. igniter replacement &mdash; different prices</li>
          <li>Gas pressure check included on every call</li>
          <li>All burners tested before we leave</li>
          <li>$89 diagnostic applied to the total</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

